o (DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.6983428).  Datasets from Discrete Molecular Dynamics are available at https://dlab.clemson.edu/research/PSD95-PSG/.</p></sec><supplementary-material><ext-link xlink:href="elife-77242-supp-v1.zip">Download zip</ext-link><p>Any figures and tables for this article are included in the PDF. The zip folder contains additional supplemental files.</p></supplementary-material></sec></back></article>